ntary resources which help parents sort out the choices without infringing on the artists'' rights to free speech, which is something that we respect.', 67943, 0), (428999, 'Assuredly, Loving Souls, you should go to God with all humility and respect, humbling yourselves in His presence, especially when you remember your past ingratitude and sins.', 67483, 0), (429000, 'I got into acting because my teachers kept nudging me into it. The power a teacher has to influence someone is so great. I can''t think of a profession I have more respect for.', 67944, 0);
