ue, the disrespect to women has got to be through. To all the mothers and the sisters and the wives and friends, I wanna offer my love and respect till the end.', 67963, 0), (429029, 'This is my advice to entrepreneurs. It''s easy to give up, but believe in your ideas. Surround yourself with people you respect and are smarter than you.', 67964, 0), (429030, 'I''m trying to demystify the whole process. Make it simple, make it palatable. I want people to have respect for the law, and I want to educate people on the basics of the law.', 67965, 0), (429031, 'When someone you have a lot of respect for believes in you, it helps you believe in yourself.', 67966, 0), (429032, 'I believe we don''t need to widen the divide between the West and Islam. Rather, we need to build dialogue to encourage tolerance and respect.', 67967, 0), (429033, 'With all due respect to arachnophobes, I love spiders. Some might call me obsessed, but I''ve been studying spiders and spider silks for many years now and don''t see an end in sight. There is simply too much to do.', 67968, 0), (429034, 'I deal with a lot of wonderful gay people. I hire a lot of them. I use a lot of them. I respect them. They''re terrific. I am good friends with them. But you live your life the way you want to live, and I''ll live mine, and I won''t stick my nose in yours.', 65113, 0), (429035, 'If guys don''t respect themselves, they don''t respect other people. That''s times and personalities. And all of them are not that way. But it don''t take but one or two to screw up the whole crowd.', 67969, 0), (429036, 'I give everyone upmost respect, and when people feel that, you end up getting the most out of your interaction with them. That connectivity is really important in my life.', 67970, 0), (429037, 'Heck, nobody gets along perfectly. But what we have is respect for one another. We have a system where one guy can veto anything.', 67971, 0), (429038, 'As long as I have the support and respect of my teammates, that''s 